---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
const phone = '+13102995555';
---
<Base title="Event Insurance — Special Event Liability (Same-Day COI) | CoverToday" description="Special event & one-day liability insurance for weddings, parties, pop-ups and vendors. Get a certificate of insurance the same day, with the venue named as additional insured. Call (310) 299-5555.">
  <section class="hero"><div class="wrap">
    <h1>Event insurance — covered today, COI in hand.</h1>
    <p class="sub">Weddings, parties, pop-ups, markets and vendor booths. Your venue needs a certificate of insurance — we issue it the same day, with them named as additional insured.</p>
  </div></section>

  <section><div class="wrap" style="max-width:820px">
    <h2 class="sec">When you need event insurance</h2>
    <p>Most venues, cities, and event organizers require a special-event liability policy (often $1M) before you can hold your event — and they want a certificate of insurance (COI) naming them as <em>additional insured</em>. Whether it's a wedding, a birthday, a corporate event, or a weekend vendor booth, we set it up fast.</p>

    <h2 class="sec">What it covers</h2>
    <ul style="line-height:2;font-size:17px">
      <li><strong>General liability</strong> — bodily injury and property damage at your event.</li>
      <li><strong>Host liquor liability</strong> — if alcohol is served.</li>
      <li><strong>Additional insured</strong> — venue/landlord added to your certificate.</li>
      <li><strong>Vendor / exhibitor coverage</strong> — for markets, fairs and pop-ups.</li>
    </ul>

    <h2 class="sec">How it works</h2>
    <ol style="line-height:2;font-size:17px">
      <li>Send us the event date, venue, headcount, and the venue's COI requirements.</li>
      <li>We quote special-event carriers and find the right limits.</li>
      <li>We bind and email your certificate — same day, additional insured included.</li>
    </ol>

    <div class="card" style="padding:26px;margin-top:24px;text-align:center">
      <h2 style="margin-top:0">Need a COI for your venue today?</h2>
      <div style="display:flex;gap:12px;justify-content:center;flex-wrap:wrap;margin-top:10px">
        <a class="btn btn-call" href={`tel:${phone}`}>📞 (310) 299-5555</a>
        <a class="btn btn-ghost" href="/quote">Get a quote →</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div></section>
</Base>
